{
  "page": "League",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>league</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Measurement#Units_of_length\" title=\"Measurement\">measure of distance</a>, equal to three miles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Known_distances\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known distances</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Westeros\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Westeros</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Essos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Essos</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_distances\">Known distances</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=League&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known distances\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Westeros\">Westeros</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=League&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Westeros\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> is a hundred league long.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mole%27s_Town\" title=\"Mole&#39;s Town\">Mole's Town</a> is half a league south of <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Gift\" title=\"Gift\">Gift</a> is composed of Brandon's Gift and the New Gift, each streching twenty five leagues.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hammerhorn\" title=\"Hammerhorn\">Hammerhorn</a> is six leagues inland.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Three leagues separate <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Water_Gardens\" title=\"Water Gardens\">Water Gardens</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Harlaw\" title=\"Rodrik Harlaw\">Rodrik Harlaw</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a> coast is four hundred leagues long.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ryman_Frey\" title=\"Ryman Frey\">Ryman Frey</a> died two leagues south of <a href=\"/index.php/Fairmarket\" title=\"Fairmarket\">Fairmarket</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Forty leagues separate Castle Black from <a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Deepwood Motte\">Deepwood Motte</a> is five leagues inland.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A hundred leagues separate Deepwood Motte from <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>On her way to the Wall, <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a> first meets <a href=\"/index.php/Ty\" title=\"Ty\">Ty</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Dannel\" title=\"Dannel\">Dannel</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> two leagues south of Mole's Town,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> then she is escorted to meet Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a> half a league south of Mole's Town.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>There is a mill controled by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Webber\" title=\"House Webber\">House Webber</a> six leagues away from their seat of <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>In the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Stonebridge\" title=\"Battle at Stonebridge\">battle at Stonebridge</a>, it is reported that the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a> ran red with blood for twenty leagues.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>During the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Dayne\" title=\"Joffrey Dayne\">Joffrey Dayne</a> burned fields, farms, and villages for twenty leagues around <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Battle at Rook&#39;s Rest\">Battle at Rook's Rest</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Meleys\" title=\"Meleys\">Meleys</a> crashed to the ground half a league away from <a href=\"/index.php/Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Longtable\" title=\"Longtable\">Longtable</a> is located some thirty leagues to the southwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tumbleton\" title=\"Tumbleton\">Tumbleton</a> is located sixty leagues to the southwest of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-17\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-17\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> and one hundred and sixty leagues to the south of <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>During the invasion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a>, the forces of King <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hoare</a> landed forty leagues south of <a href=\"/index.php/Seagard\" title=\"Seagard\">Seagard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> has been measured as almost two leagues long from west to east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_casterly_rock.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_casterly_rock.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Essos\">Essos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=League&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Essos\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> burnt every tree within twenty leagues of their city before the arrival of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_20-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-20\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_21-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-21\">&#91;20&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Five hundred leagues separate Meereen from <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_22-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-22\">&#91;21&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> cities are linked by the old Ghiscari coast road; a hundred leagues from <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a> and fifty leagues from Yunkai to Meereen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_23-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-23\">&#91;22&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_River\" title=\"Warden of the River\">Warden of the River</a> is in charge of all the ferries, dredges, and irrigation ditches along the <a href=\"/index.php/Skahazadhan\" title=\"Skahazadhan\">Skahazadhan</a> for fifty leagues from Meereen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_24-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-24\">&#91;23&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The largest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jhala\" title=\"Jhala\">Jhala</a>, stretches two hundred leagues from tip to tip.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_25-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-25\">&#91;24&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_Sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dothraki Sea\">Dothraki Sea</a> stretches more than seven hundred leagues from the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a> in the west to the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> in the east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_26-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-26\">&#91;25&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The Bone Mountains stretches more than five hundred leagues from north to south and a hundred leagues from east to west.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_27-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-27\">&#91;26&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Far_Ib\" title=\"Far Ib\">Far Ib</a> lies more than a hundred leagues southeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Ib\" title=\"Ib\">Ib</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_28-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-28\">&#91;27&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=League&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-17\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-17\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The distance between Tumbleton and King's Landing is cited three times in the books: \"sixty leagues\" (in <i>The World of Ice and Fire, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon II</i>), \"some fifty leagues\" (in <i>Fire and Blood, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant</i>), and \"sixty leagues\" (in <i>Fire and Blood, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant</i>). It can be reasonably assumed the distance is actually sixty leagues and the passage referencing fifty leagues was a broad estimation.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=League&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, The King's Prize.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thro